<section class="services-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="services-intro">
      <div>
        <div class="label">Services in full</div>
        <h2>One company — seven specialties.</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Brunaþéttingar provide <strong>complete technical insulation</strong> for buildings across Iceland. We started in fire sealing in 2011 and have added services as our clients have required — always with the same focus on quality, certification and documentation.</p>
        <p>These are the seven areas we serve today. Some services overlap (fire protection and acoustic insulation use the same materials) and some require specialised systems from Isogenopak, WrapTec or Armaflex — but they all fall under technical insulation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- for s in services %}
    <article class="service-feature{% if loop.index0 % 2 == 1 %} flip{% endif %}">
      <div class="pic{% if s.imageContain %} contain{% endif %}">
        <img src="{{ s.image }}" alt="" width="1200" height="900">
      </div>
      <div class="copy">
        <span class="num-badge">{{ s.number }} / {{ s.category[lang] }}</span>
        <h2>{{ s.title[lang] | safe }}</h2>
        <p class="lead">{{ s.lead[lang] | safe }}</p>
        <div class="insight">
          <strong>{{ s.insightStrong[lang] }}</strong>
          {{ s.insight[lang] | safe }}
        </div>
        <ul class="bullets">
          {%- for b in s.bullets[lang] %}
          <li>{{ b | safe }}</li>
          {%- endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="value-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div>
        <div class="label">Cost effectiveness</div>
        <h2>Technical insulation that <span class="ul">pays itself back</span>.</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Technical insulation is one of the most cost-effective investments a building owner can make. The <strong>Isogenopak</strong> and <strong>WrapTec</strong> systems we install are particularly economical — they multiply the lifespan of the underlying insulation, reduce maintenance costs and improve energy efficiency over the entire operating life of the building.</p>
        <p>We provide an annual energy-saving calculation for every project before you accept the quote — so you know exactly when the investment will pay itself back.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

